These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, snowboarding
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, march
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, go
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, bus, scooter
House: modern, craftsman, palace
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, montecristo, bongani
 1. the person driving the van is not the person playing billiard##6
 2. the modern house is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 4. the palace house is somewhere between the person who's sport is parkour and the bongani-smoker##7
 5. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 7. the person playing go is not the craftsman house##6
 8. the modern house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 9. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing go##1
10. the bongani-smoker is not the person playing go##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| Sport      | parkour       | volleyball  | snowboarding     |
| Birthday          | march       | august  | february    |
| Game         | mah-jongg  | go   | billiard |
| Transport   | van | scooter   | bus     |
| House   | modern  | palace | craftsman   |
| Cigar           | montecristo  | tiparillo      | bongani  |

