The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, train
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, august, september
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person who growsbegonia##7
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 6. the person who growspoppy is between the person driving the scooter and the person watching scientific movies##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the person traveling to boston##7
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking tea is not the person driving the scooter##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |      3       |
