3. the person playing go is not the person traveling to edinburgh##6
4. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person playing mah-jongg##6
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
7. the person who's sport is handball is the person who growsorchid##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person traveling to hamburg and the owner of the horse##7
9. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hamburg##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |      3      |
| Pet      | hedgehog       | ferret      | horse    |
| City          | hamburg     | edinburgh        | marseilles        |
| Flower           | sunflower  | orchid | poppy   |
| Game   | domino | mah-jongg           | go |
| Sport   | badminton  | handball    | weightlifting   |
| Hobby     | sudoku        | gardening          | video-games         |

