There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, red, brown
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, baking, singing
3 different games are played: domino, scrabble, bridge
 1. the fan country is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 3. the person who likes pink is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who likes brown##7
 4. the fan metal is the person traveling to paris##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person traveling to paris##1
 6. the person who likes pink is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fan country##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
10. the person who likes pink is the person traveling to london##1
11. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5

.:: Answer ::.
